data.description: Welcome to the lovely community of "Crestview Meadows". This Beautiful Northeast Newer Construction home is located on a cul-de-sac. Centrally located to everything. This nice home features high ceilings in living, dining and bedroom areas. 18x18 tile throughout the house except the bedrooms. Sliding doors at the dining room & master bedroom leading to the backyard. Backyard is on a mountain & has a slope uphill. Espresso cabinets in kitchen with granite coutertops, steel appliances: stove, dishwasher & microwave. Washer, Dryer & refrigerator are also included. Walk-in pantry room in kitchen. L-shaped hallway leading to all three bedrooms. Laundry area located inside home in the hallway. One of two full baths located in the hallway. 2 car garage attached to home. 2 walk-in closets in the master bedroom. Two nice size bedrooms. Five system included. Gutters throughout home. Beautiful newer home equipped with all modern features & ready to be moved into. Newer built from 2016. One owner.
